Package com.nmoumoulidis.opensensor.restInterface

Class Summary
BatchDataRetrieveService A key class of the system.
BatchDataSendToServerServiceHelper The second key class that utilizes the phone as an data aggregator between the OpenSensor Station and Server.
SensorListRestRequestRunnable Extends Runnable in order to run in its own Java Thread for speed, retrieving the list of available sensors on the connected OpenSensor Station.
SensorStationRestRequestTask An Android AsyncTask for all the REST (GET and PUT) requests (except the batch-data request and sensor-list request) that are performed towards the OpenSensor Station.
SensorStationRestResponseHandler Handles the responses from REST requests that SensorStationRestRequestTask makes.
ServerRestRequestTask An Android AsyncTask for all the REST GET requests that are performed towards the OpenSensor Server, while providing visual feedback to the user.
ServerRestResponseHandler Handles the responses from REST requests that ServerRestRequestTask makes.
